Class DereferencingTaskQueue

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      de.fuberlin.wiwiss.ng4j.semwebclient.threadutils.TaskQueueBase
          de.fuberlin.wiwiss.ng4j.semwebclient.DereferencingTaskQueue
All Implemented Interfaces:
DereferencingListener, Runnable
public class DereferencingTaskQueue
extends TaskQueueBase
implements DereferencingListener

The DereferencingTaskQueue is a thread which observes the DereferencerThreads. It starts all DereferencerThreads tries to assign new tasks to free DereferencerThreads and interrupts them if the timeout is reached.

Author:
Tobias Gauß, Olaf Hartig, Hannes Mühleisen
